titlestmt.titleproper: Guide to the Senior Honor Essays of Yale Students
Senior Honor Essays of Yale Students
titlestmt.author: compiled by Staff of Manuscripts and Archives

publicationstmt.publisher: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on Thursday January 10, 2019 at 11:36

did.unittitle: Senior honor essays of Yale students

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The materials consist of a selected collection of essays written by Yale seniors to meet graduation requirements in various departments.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 47 (YRG 47), Collections documenting teaching and learning in Yale academic programs.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University. Written permission of the author is required for photocopying.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Senior Honor Essays of Yale Students (RU 118). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged in two series: I. Alphabetical. II. Numerical.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of a selected collection of essays written by Yale seniors to meet graduation requirements in various departments.
